  "title": "Business Development Executive (CyberSecurity) - Up to $6000",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>- Contributing to the business development team for the growth of cyber-security businesses in Singapore and the APAC region. <br />- S/He is expected to possess keen eye to spot opportunities and able to execute quickly on tasks given. <br />- S/He should be able to do consultative sales either independently or by leveraging available and accessible technical resources to develop new businesses.<br />- Cold calling, Emailing, Road shows, events and other corporate means to secure new business<br /><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>- Degree in Cybersecurity, Computer Science, Business Management, Business Administration, or a related field.<br />- Minimum 1 to 3 years of experience in business development, sales or client relationship management, preferably in a corporate or customer-facing environment.<br />- Ability to adapt quickly and able to embrace potentially steep learning curve.<br />- Possess an innovative and open mind-set especially in the creation of viable partnerships and new markets with radically differentiated propositions.<br />- A well-natured, result-oriented, self-motivating, self-driven team player.<br />- Sensitive to numbers and good with various tools like Microsoft Excel, Word and PowerPoint.<br />- Ability to work independently and execute the tasks given efficiently.<br />- Fresh graduates with relevant qualifications or internship experience are also welcome to apply.<br /><br /><br /><strong>Interested and suitable candidate kindly click quick apply. Resume will be forwarded to Stepfan Soon Yit</strong></p><p><strong>We regret that only suitable candidate will be notified.</strong></p><p><strong>GEMS Recruit/EA License : 23C1459</strong></p><p><strong>EA Personnel No : R24120893 (Stepfan Soon Yit)</strong></p>",
